  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_docstructbench_llm-raw-scihub-o.O-j.snb.2004.06.022.pdf_2_2",
    "text": "Fig. 1. Real structure consisting of three thin layers: silver (for electric contact), metal-free phthalocyanine and palladium fabricated on an alundum substrate.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.0676344213583858,
      0.17144134159532262,
      0.47398099232838353,
      0.21098776796730706
