    "order": 13
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_docstructbench_llm-raw-scihub-o.O-j.snb.2004.06.022.pdf_2_7",
    "text": "The main goal of this paper is to investigate the electric resistance of a layered phthalocyanine and palladium (Pc + Pd) structure under the influence of various hydrogen concentrations in nitrogen and air. We show that during the",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.06769826686783295,
      0.23982558097143564,
      0.4758220428461908,
      0.30087209254809116
    ],
    "page": "docstructbench_llm-raw-scihub-o.O-j.snb.2004.06.022.pdf_2",
    "order": 14
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_docstructbench_llm-raw-scihub-o.O-j.snb.2004.06.022.pdf_2_12",
    "text": "interaction of hydrogen with bilayer structures metal-free phthalocyanine and palladium there occurs a strong change in the resistance of these structures. This would correspond to an acousto-electric effect in the SAW sensor system",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
